\n    $3000<br />\n<br />\n7) 更換吊燈 (大概7盞): <br />\n    $2000"},{"pid":"aa63a2beae8743da78df42abdc8ee3b5a6e5be05","tid":2508670,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"6) 更換全屋燈掣&amp;SOCKET(未知幾多個):<br />\n$3000<br />\n<br />\n好抵 出面講緊850一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />斷估你屋企都多過3個掛"},{"pid":"e1a5cca48cb6a17e8d5058607d057f868cbafbe8","tid":2508670,"uid":117261,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:43:54.000Z","msg":"買到7百呎單位，就唔差在比indoor design幫你設計啦<br />\n你有咩要求，有咩dream 邊個位落socket都可以同佢地講，<br />\n佢地會整到你心水既house<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔放心比佢地「建議」既工程公司做，可以買斷佢圖紙<br />\n然後自行搵工程公司做，自己選料"},{"pid":"6162fe0a5a3f596b59b8cc1e5ae1cc0044c7a036","tid":2508670,"uid":48652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa63a2beae8743da78df42abdc8ee3b5a6e5be05","tid":2508670,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"6) 更換全屋燈掣&amp;SOCKET(未知幾多個):<br />\n$3000<br />\n<br />\n好抵 出面講緊850一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />斷估你屋企都多過3個掛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"我鳩估架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />~<br />\n$850個咁貴架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a1c609a7573d50ae069c60ca4a4692dfbeb177","tid":2508670,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6162fe0a5a3f596b59b8cc1e5ae1cc0044c7a036","tid":2508670,"uid":48652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa63a2beae8743da78df42abdc8ee3b5a6e5be05","tid":2508670,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"6) 更換全屋燈掣&amp;SOCKET(未知幾多個):<br />\n$3000<br />\n<br />\n好抵 出面講緊850一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />斷估你屋企都多過3個掛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"我鳩估架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji